This is a simple web-based Rock Paper Scissors game created using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. 
Players can choose between rock, paper, or scissors and play against the computer. 
The game determines the winner based on traditional rules:

Rock beats Scissors
Scissors beats Paper
Paper beats Rock
Features:
Interactive UI with neon gaming theme.
Displays the result after each round.


How to Play:
Choose Rock, Paper, or Scissors.
The computer will randomly select its choice.
The result will be displayed on the screen.
